Purpose:	Function set the outline font to be used in the TextArea.  The following constants are defined:
{FCode}TextArea_DefaultFont   "Corpus.Medium"
TextArea_DefaultHeight (12 * 16)
TextArea_DefaultWidth  (12 * 16)
